  "description": "<p><strong>Position title : Sales Executive( Retail Sales)</strong></p><p>Location: Jalan Besar</p><p>Working Days: 5.5 days a week (Must be able to work on weekends)</p><p>Working hours : 11am to 9pm</p><p>Salary : $3,100 basic+ Comm</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Requirement</strong></p><ul><li>Candidate with retail or jewellery experience is an added advantage</li><li>Minimum GCE “N” level</li></ul><p><strong>Job Scope</strong></p><ul><li>Understand and be able to explain to customers the range of Jewelley the company has to offer</li><li>Promote the various products, services and schemes to customers</li><li>Attend to customers and ensure service delivery standards are met in achieving total customer satisfaction</li><li>Achieve monthly sales targets.</li><li>Ensure merchandise and displays are consistently well presented and displayed</li><li>Manage and maintain the overall positive image of the showroom</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Interested applicants, WA your resume to ‪‪‪+65 9136 9792‬‬‬ or email your resume to supreme.yentan@gmail.com.</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>TAN YEN ZHEN (CHEN YANZHEN) REG NO: R25138932</p><p>THE SUPREMEHR ADVISORY PTE LTD EA NO: 14C7279</p>",
